ing: 8 ounces chive and onion cream cheese
des: "A quick and easy dip that everyone loves. Doubling the recipe yields enough for a party. It is great with plain chips or nachos. Sliced black olives may be used as an additional topping."
ins: In a bowl, combine the sour cream, cream cheese and taco seasoning. Spread the mixture into a pie dish. Sprinkle the Cheddar cheese over the mixture in an even layer. Top the cheese with the tomatoes and green onions.
